Privacy Policy
If you create an account in our games, we may ask for personal information such as an email to link your account for logging in. This information will only be used for security and password reset.
You can delete your email from our database by deleting your account, changing the email in settings, or emailing
info@minidragon.net
with a request to delete your account and remove your personal information.
We may revise this privacy policy in the future by posting the changes here.
